<% pay_subscription = params[:pay_subscription] %>
<% trial_ends_at = pay_subscription&.trial_ends_at %>
<% charge_date = pay_subscription&.current_period_end %>
Hi,

Your TheraSaurus free trial ends<% if trial_ends_at %> on <%= l trial_ends_at.to_date, format: :long %><% else %> soon<% end %>.

<% if charge_date %>
Your card will be charged on <%= l charge_date.to_date, format: :long %> unless you cancel before then.
<% else %>
Your card will be charged when your trial ends, unless you cancel before then.
<% end %>

To manage or cancel your subscription, visit your Membership settings:
<%= membership_url %>

Thanks for trying TheraSaurus.
